title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - October 19, 2021
itunes:title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - October 19, 2021
description:
Mark and Gary link up to discuss the latest in the Alex Murdaugh saga as well as the developments coming out of the January 6th Commission and witnesses ignoring their subpoenas. 

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
